<div style="text-align: center;"><b>About Us</b></div><div><br></div><div style="text-align: justify;">Rush Cargo is a business partnership in Zamboanga between 2 very good friends with&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 1rem;">impressive experience in airline services. Originally, it was named as Jet Cargo Aviation Services from&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">2001 to 2010 which only caters airport to airport transfers with fruits, veggies and marine products as&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 1rem;">their main commodity.</span></div><div style="text-align: justify;">In 2011 the company was renamed to Rush Cargo which implies speed of delivery service. It&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 1rem;">also ventured into door-to- door delivery in the region of Zamboanga City.</span></div>